{"tid":1951742,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股市崩盤引發散戶興趣 「如何買股票」成 Google熱門關鍵字","createTime":"2020-03-31T07:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T07:56:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"015dc541ee0d2014461866f1886bb1c673956199","tid":1951742,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"2020-03-31 14:01<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕受到武漢肺炎疫情影響，美股在過去幾週歷經暴漲暴跌、落入熊市。不過隨著股市的崩盤，也引發散戶投資者對於學習如何購買股票感到極大的興趣。引用Google搜尋趨勢（Google Trends）數據顯示，近2週來「如何購買股票（how to buy stocks）」成為Google搜尋熱門關鍵字。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，據Google搜尋趨勢數據顯示，「如何購買股票（how to buy stocks）」近2週來，躍升成為Google搜尋熱門關鍵字，搜尋次數激增，為過去幾個月來每週平均值的10倍之多。意味著，散戶投資者迫切希望避免錯過最近1次下跌的機會。<br />\n<br />\n此外，同樣在近期被熱搜得關鍵字還有「道瓊工業平均指數」、「失業」、「在家上班」與「快遞」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3118413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3118413&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=cc19a471\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3118413&h=e2daf890\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3118413</a>"},{"pid":"bb45ab1efa7d83d43824d7e986ee8c8c3b6c9e35","tid":1951742,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"爆煲啊入市啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fbd8b2f76b3b743342b8840784b2c93ceb83f2","tid":1951742,"uid":222978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88QuAUy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88QuAUy.png&h=3fdfd2c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次爆邊前熱門度都係peak<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a81927a9a91141c9aaba28324482a164a5b7986","tid":1951742,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29fbd8b2f76b3b74334